<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="text-align: center; font-size: 90%; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa; line-height: 1.5em;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Hauling_supplies_on_Attu.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Hauling supplies on Attu.jpg" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0b/Hauling_supplies_on_Attu.jpg/300px-Hauling_supplies_on_Attu.jpg" width="300" height="200" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0b/Hauling_supplies_on_Attu.jpg/450px-Hauling_supplies_on_Attu.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/0b/Hauling_supplies_on_Attu.jpg 2x" /></a><br />
American troops hauling supplies on <a href="Attu_Island" title="Attu Island">Attu</a> in May 1943 through Jarmin pass. Their vehicles could not move across the island's rugged terrain.</td>
</tr>
